:"Carácter excepcional","guid":"AUtghz8hTmGTnUZvEpel2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"256","text":"PRESTACIÓN ASISTENTE PERSONAL","guid":"FqEt42HISGOOpPWdQoOrng","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Asistente profesional contratado","guid":"eSExazORSmOjrSuwouR_-w","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"Promueve autonomía → trabajo, educación, vida autónoma","guid":"mSL09miASlS47QiHsGlJkQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"223","text":"OTROS RECURSOS","guid":"McOq_I24Sqy9drdHGT2hlQ","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"RESPIRO FAMILIAR → CD fin de semana, residencia temporal","guid":"MmM-Q1GpR52pOmCgvQaEOA","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"PRÉSTAMO productos apoyo → cama articulada, grúa","guid":"_WHV4-ESQt-Ucmpv96nAlg","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"266","text":"\"CUIDAR AL CUIDADOR\" → información + apoyo + grupos ayuda","guid":"dFjmxK-MRRi60sIgcS4s8w","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"266","text":"COMIDA A DOMICILIO (dieta avalada)","guid":"hoYRqGKVTeKBCVXQxvWwZw","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"266","text":"LAVANDERÍA","guid":"8GPGmF1_SNaoKOQCyc-utQ","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"266","text":"AYUDAS HABITABILIDAD VIVIENDA","guid":"BfRBT7zHQB27l3-XHHuKww","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"223","text":"ASOCIACIONES TERCER SECTOR","guid":"K2RFzKrpTzOZTWkqhSS4Tw","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"AECC, AFAs (Alzheimer), Cáritas, Cruz Roja","guid":"6jZji1_-RnirjH56PXOIew","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"223","text":"EQUIVALENTES CHILE","guid":"2CUHPUaHSmC9DtuC_gMxvg","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"SENAMA → Servicio Nacional del Adulto Mayor","guid":"aICoCFPUSb-817gIxh6eyQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"Programa Cuidados Domiciliarios SENAMA","guid":"LQ2LkltWR1Wcisn6QBOiQg","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"ELEAM (Establecimientos Larga Estadía)","guid":"1Rfnm7LySDCa3YCyWg5hAQ","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"275","text":"Centros Día del AM SENAMA","guid":"3rlnIOdRS6mkJRVmPQohUg","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"275","text":"Sin BVD formal → evaluación por VGI + EFAM","guid":"CL7DsaftSYeQCO96XS5wLQ","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"275","text":"Sin derecho subjetivo universal equivalente","guid":"mNGwY2XSTpSVeGz3Z1Y6gg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"282","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"CVz-8GJdR_SoUA6N00P4GQ","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"5 CORRECTOS + 6° = DOCUMENTAR la administración → previene errores en cascada","guid":"9l7mZwDbQFKuum3xYbOpbw","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"CORTICOIDES INHALADOS → SIEMPRE enjuague boca + bicarbonato → ↓ candidiasis","guid":"nq2j3XB3Tu6YpGX-MPt7lQ","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"282","text":"HIPÉRICO es el inductor enzimático \"natural\" más peligroso → ↓ Sintrom, ↓ digoxina, ↓ ACOs, ↓ antirretrovirales","guid":"JBE-1hyiQWi20HaufyWenA","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"282","text":"COVID ATÍPICO EN AM FRÁGIL → DELIRIUM + febrícula + anorexia + caídas → fiebre presente <50% en >80a","guid":"r-z-nuiOQTKN1Zs9PLqrmA","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"282","text":"NO TRITURAR (mnemo GRACE) → Gelatina, Retardada, Acción entérica, Comprimidos efervescentes, Sublinguales","guid":"-2T1Xrx4R6SyCReEl_VQBQ","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"282","text":"DUELO ANTICIPADO no reconocido = PREDICTOR de duelo complicado (intervención pre-mortem NNT ~8)","guid":"MWwKlbiOSo2ZCN2Ajzbp9Q","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"282","text":"INSTRUCCIONES PREVIAS prevalecen sobre opinión familiar. Chile → Ley 20.584 art. 14 permite rechazo (sin registro nacional)","guid":"gXb0CzwzRviguwrodv49ag","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"282","text":"LEY 8/2021 → fin modelo SUSTITUTIVO → modelo de APOYO. Procesos previos revisables de oficio","guid":"yUotJKLLSJuBG-P7CxFRbw","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"282","text":"BVD 25+ = dependencia moderada; GRADO III mortalidad 1 año ~40% → discutir objetivos de cuidado","guid":"LcX-dpINQxeYff8fIxn3Lg","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"282","text":"SOBRECARGA cuidador (Zarit >46) = PREDICTOR independiente de institucionalización (OR ~3) y mortalidad del AM","guid":"EZ9bsS1iRnymXZD_BBv3Uw","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"282","text":"RESPIRO familiar → ↓ sobrecarga + retrasa institucionalización (mínimo 2 sem/año o 1 d/sem en CD)","guid":"XKi3bfAmSRWnHgmXJHplLg","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"282","text":"Referencias","guid":"54vsNJZIR5Wh6nIw33oMAw","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"1. SEGG. Curso cuidadores PM dependencia. Temas 18-22. Madrid; 2023. ISBN 978-84-09-47741-8.","guid":"j07uOoOWR92od3UHm27eTQ","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"2. Ley 8/2021, de 2 de junio, reforma legislación civil y procesal para apoyo a personas con discapacidad. BOE núm. 132, 3 jun 2021.","guid":"dAqGicibRFWB8-ZspjrxnA","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"3. Ley 39/2006, de 14 de diciembre, Promoción de la Autonomía Personal y Atención a la Dependencia. BOE núm. 299, 15 dic 2006.","guid":"5axqs71_SX6BazmwmAQzIg","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"4. Convención Internacional sobre los Derechos de las Personas con Discapacidad. ONU; 2006. Ratificada por España 2008.","guid":"A73JE8x5S9OlngK9Gr3ZDA","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"294","text":"5. Kübler-Ross E. On Death and Dying. New York: Macmillan; 1969.","guid":"FVEx9K6bT2qIicZq1qxgdA","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"294","text":"6. Ministerio de Sanidad (España). Información COVID-19. www.sanidad.gob.es","guid":"21lkhu71QsmoAjSlBsf1pA","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"294","text":"7. Ley 21.331/2021 reconocimiento y protección de los derechos de las personas en atención de salud mental. Chile.","guid":"Fx6lsYanTaymVql7cr7mng","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":301,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Cuidados-Domicilio","filename":"04-Cuidados-Especiales-Contexto-Social","id":"map_932","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"04-Cuidados-Especiales-Contexto-Social"}